description:
Expand your track list with the Best of 80's Vol. 2 Song Pack!  You need the full game Let's Sing Country to use this DLC. Includes hit songs:
• Wham! "Wake Me Up Before You Go-Go"
• Communards "Don't Leave Me This Way"
• Roxette "It Must Have Been Love"
• Bonnie Tyler "Total Eclipse Of The Heart"
• Kim Wilde "Kids In America"
name: Let's Sing - Best of 80's Vol. 2 Song Pack
